OL,3,CSteve Bruce to miss Blackpool match
OL,4,Cafter death of baby grandson
OL,6,FSteve Bruce will miss Blackpool FC's
OL,7,Fclash against Barnsley following the
OL,8,F"tragic" death of his baby grandson.
OL,10,FBlackpool confirmed their 63-year-old
OL,11,Fboss, whose former clubs include
OL,12,FBirmingham, Hull, Aston Villa and
OL,13,FNewcastle, would not be in the dugout
OL,14,Fon Saturday afternoon.
OL,16,FA Blackpool statement said: "The club
OL,17,Fcan announce that head coach Steve
OL,18,FBruce will not be in attendance at
OL,19,Ftomorrow's fixture against Barnsley
OL,20,Fdue to the tragic passing of his four-
OL,21,Fmonth-old grandson Madison.
