OL,6,F"We are with you every step of the
OL,7,Fway, Smudger," Millwall said on X,
OL,8,Fwhile QPR added: "We're all with you
OL,9,FSmudger."
OL,11,FSmith retired in the summer after a
OL,12,Fspell with Salford, whose assistant
OL,13,Fmanager Alex Bruce, Steve's son and
OL,14,FMadison's uncle, will also be absent
OL,15,Ffor Saturday's League Two match at
OL,16,FCrawley.
OL,18,FA statement from Salford said: "All at
OL,19,Fthe football club send our love and
OL,20,Ffull support to Alex, Matt Smith and
OL,21,Fthe family.
